history.content:
This is a reminder that midnight tomorrow (Wednesday, Sept 12th) is the deadline for adding or dropping classes.

Please be aware that EECS will not process any requests for F18 received after 4pm on Wednesday Sept 12th. We need time to process the requests that come in at the last minute before the midnight deadline. This includes research units, concurrent enrollment processing, permission codes, or time conflicts.

You are still welcome to add or drop yourself from classes until midnight but if you encounter difficulties in adding or dropping unfortunately, we will not be able to help you.
history.subject: Tomorrow (Sept 12th) is the last day to add or drop classes!
